::Prowl::

Prowl spirals again, a few shots digging into his side. So far, he had kept 
the femm in his arms from any harm, but with the enemies continuing to fire, 
it wouldn't be too long untill they were caught.

Prowl speeds up as he sees Dinobot enter the forest. Now that Dinobot and Tav 
were on the move, escape was closer.
